706080f-a.text:
Nostrand Ave., east side, between Myrtle and Vernon Aves. This view is taken,looking southeast. The house at the left, faces on Vernon Ave. The orchard is all that remains of the Boerum farm.
About 191O.
Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
